fields.name: INFO_DBSNP
fields.desc: dbSNP version which established the rs_id

fields.name: INFO_AA_AGE
fields.desc: Esitmated Variant Age in kilo years for the African American Population

fields.name: INFO_AA_GTC
fields.desc: African American Genotype Counts in the order of listed GTS

fields.name: REF
fields.desc: The value in the POS field refers to the position of the first base in the String.

fields.name: INFO_GTC
fields.desc: Total Genotype Counts in the order of listed GTS

fields.name: INFO_EA_AGE
fields.desc: Esitmated Variant Age in kilo years for the European American Population

fields.name: INFO_GTS
fields.desc: Observed Genotypes. For INDELs, A1, A2, or An refers to the N-th alternate allele while R refers to the reference allele.

fields.name: INFO_GRCh38_POSITION
fields.desc: GRCh38 chromosomal postion liftover from the original GRCh37 chromosomal position. A value of -1 means the GRCh37 position can not be mapped to the GRCh38 build.

fields.name: INFO_ID
fields.desc: indels mapping predicted with SeattleSeqAnnotation137 on dbSNP v137

fields.name: INFO_EA_GTC
fields.desc: European American Genotype Counts in the order of listed GTS

fields.name: ALT
fields.desc: Comma separated list of alternate non-reference alleles called on at least one of the samples.
